values: Dr 's visit went well, I lost 6 pounds in 3 weeks! The Ear Nose Throat Dude was very nice and very efficient. We are going to attack this infection aggressively, I even got a shot in me bum! I have another anti biotic, since I was done with the other. I will be taking augmentin, a nose spray called astelin which is an antihistamine spray, and a double does of medrol which is an oral steroid. I expect to be talking like, and have muscles like Arnold Swarchenegger by the end of this. (It's not a tumor!) Thank you everyone, you've been very supportive during all this sickness stuff I keep posting. A couple of you guessed the song correctly, so I give 10 points to each of you; , and . I have no idea what you are going to do with the 10 points, maybe I'll do a 'Name That Tune" contest in the future ;) {{hugs}} all around :D
